CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: MSC Income Fund Inc is a non-diversified closed-end management investment company. The investment objective is to generate current income through debt and equity investments and the secondary objective is to generate long-term capital appreciation through such investments. The company invests in senior secured term loans, second lien loans and mezzanine debt and selected equity investments issued by lower middle-market and middle-market companies.
